<br>
The entire server IS first-come, first-serve.  That is a fact.  What the server population votes is irrelevant.  This whole reservation system exists because those with power ALLOW it to exist.  You know who that is?  It's the large guilds, the so-called &quot;uber&quot; guilds that people seem to like to trash so often.  It's SR, Watchers, LoH, Enshadowed, Drac, GoTR, PA, Elysian, and so on, who allow this system to exist.  These guilds (and in some cases with their &quot;allies&quot;) are self-sufficient.  We don't NEED reservations and in our day-to-day raiding, we normally don't use them.<br>
<br>
Temple of Veeshan.  North, West, and East.  None of which are reservable and yet most of these guilds hit those areas.  You know how we work it out?  We just do.  If we go in and another guild is there, we talk to the other guild and try to work it out.  And we do.  Sometimes we compromise, sometimes we're sh*t out of luck because they were there first.  But we don't have any of these stupid boards and reservations.<br>
<br>
How does this affect you?  A number of ways.  I'll use my guild as an example.<br>
<br>
Fear.  I need the item from the Shissar and so do a few in my guild.  It would be simple to go in ahead of your guild, do a portal break and wipe out the entire zone in under 2 hours.  We take the shissar, I get my epic piece and when your raid logs on, you have an empty zone.  We could, but we dont.<br>
<br>
And any of the guilds I mentioned above and more could do that.  Why?  because we're self-sufficient.  We don't NEED other guilds.  We like other guilds, but we don't NEED them and they don't need us.<br>
<br>
Want to know something else?  Every other server is like the way I just posted.  Brell, thankfully, is different.<br>
<br>
So why does the reservation system exist?  Because a lot of people a lot more powerful than you (and me) ALLOW it to exist.  Because Brell has a bunch of very nice people on it and there is no guild full of a-holes that is bent on ruining anyone's fun.<br>
<br>
So get off this attitude that you're somehow entitled to anything.  Be thankful that there are still parts of the server that ARE reservable.  I know I am.<br>
<br>
I don't think you realize just how lucky we are on Brell. <p><IMG SRC=http://members.home.net/apprentice791/LissetSig.jpg>
