<br>
I can understand how some people would see it that way and I apologize.  Long before this poll was made I questioned the validity of the FG reservation in the Mod section of this board.  I gave my reasons then for my feelings and was asked to not make a judgement until later. But then polls were made in General that would have only caused more problems and so Jaradis made this series of polls.  I used this poll to help prove the point that I had made earlier in the Mods section and got the other mods to agree with me that action should be taken.<br>
<br>
I am sorry if you all feel I jumped the gun in doing this, and I am sorry if you feel that your right to choose what was reservable and what was not was taken away.  I am also sorry if you all feel mislead by the fact that I used the poll to help prove a point.  I never meant to make anyone feel like their trust in my actions as a mod is misplaced.<br>
<br>
I only have the greatest respect for this board and the reservation system, that is why I wanted the Fire Giants removed.  If things stay on the system &quot;just because they have always been there&quot; then they will lead the system into a complete failure.  When mobs were put onto a reservation  system they were never voted on to be added (barring FG's I think they are the only one that this was not the case with) so I didn't see why, when they were not being utilized, we needed a vote to prove that the system was broken in their case.<br>
<br>
The reason no one knew in public what my feelings were is that I support the system completely, and feel that when changes need to be made the first place they should be discussed is between the Mods.  If I came to an open forum and said that the reservation system is broken a lot of people would read things into my words that are untrue.  I support any decsion made on these boards concerning the reservations, or any other change.  Even if I do not agree with them, I will support them as a Moderator.  <br>
<br>
Again I apologize for anyone's misunderstanding of what happened.  If anyone would like to talk to me on this issue you can email me at kestrithebard@hotmail.com and I would be happy to discuss my findings and the reasons I felt that the system was failing in respect to the Fire giant reservation system.<br>
